column5: Yup good to go. You taking me?   Information aint free ya know.
Thanks Brian , were in my dads boat 16 ft tinner ,  might be a little tight with four. But your welcome anytime on my big boat down on lake ontairo this spring/summer.
No worries. I,ll be talking to the gate master. The launch will be closed saturday. Saturday only though. LMAO  Have fun out there and be safe.
If the fishings hot we might go back out Sunday
